02:42:49,050 --> 02:42:52,554
go back to the house, wait for my call.
it's important.

1408
02:42:53,680 --> 02:42:56,016
i'll only be a couple of days.

1409
02:43:12,365 --> 02:43:14,534
we're on our way to brooklyn.

1410
02:43:16,703 --> 02:43:20,499
