02:45:40,805 --> 02:45:43,141
so is philip tattaglia.

1427
02:45:44,351 --> 02:45:45,852
moe greene.

1428
02:45:46,811 --> 02:45:50,607
strachi. cuneo.

1429
02:45:52,525 --> 02:45:57,864
